      "updated": 1780215146
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c0b",
      "text": "from [2026/05/26]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c0c",
      "text": "[Cosense Personal Access Token]！？！？！？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215157
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c0d",
      "text": " https://scrapbox.io/settings/personal-access-tokens",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c0e",
      "text": " [/shokai/AI生成したコードを完全に理解すべき状況と、する必要ない状況の判別方法 (2026/5時点)#6a12f3420000000000320cd4]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c0f",
      "text": " なにそれ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c10",
      "text": " いつの間にそんなの生えてたの？？？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c11",
      "text": " [connect.sid]を代替できるかも！",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c12",
      "text": " \t書き込みは引き続きできない感じか[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c13",
      "text": " \t ビジネスプランのService Accountの個人版のような感じ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c14",
      "text": " \t `PersonalAccessTokenNotAllowedError: This endpoint is not available via Personal Access Token.`というエラーが存在するので一部APIも明示的に弾いている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c15",
      "text": " \t  read系のみにしている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c16",
      "text": " \t  なるほど「非公開のプロジェクトをAIに読ませたい」的な話でconnect.sidを使われてフリーダムになるよりreadに特化したトークンを出そうという設計判断なのか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c17",
      "text": " 👀[meganii.icon][yosider.icon][sta.icon][terang.icon][mtane0412.icon][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1bed640000000000d94c18",
      "text": "\tようやく来てくれたか[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1780215141,
      "updated": 1780215141
    },
